  "title": "Facilities Engineer (Building Services)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Oversee the maintenance of building structures, both inside and outside.</li>\n  <li>Carry out repairs and upkeep of fixtures, fittings, and other building components.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with vendors for inspection, servicing, and certification of lifts, cranes, and related equipment.</li>\n  <li>Manage and supervise contractors to ensure timely and quality work.</li>\n  <li>Ensure proper care and general maintenance of the premises and surrounding areas.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma in Mechanical or Electrical Engineering.</li>\n  <li>At least 3 years of experience in <strong>facilities/building maintenance.</strong></li>\n  <li>Practical, hands-on skills in building repair and maintenance work.</li>\n  <li>Basic understanding of both mechanical and electrical systems.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p>\n<p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></p>\n<p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p>\n<p>Registration: R1326740</p>",
